snippet.title: Odinfall - Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Watch as enemies get destroyed by a Viking Moose and more fearsome heroes in this action-packed announcement trailer for Odinfall, an upcoming Viking-themed, roguelite twin-stick shooter game coming to Steam Early Access in summer 2023. A closed alpha will be available starting April 10, 2023.

#GameTrailers #Gaming
